    </div>
</main>

<div class="content">
    <section id="about" class="section pb-0">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <header class="text-center col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                    <h2 class="section-title-2">Who is Virgo?</h2>
                    <div class="about-entry text-center">
                        <p>In efforts to expand our horizons, we welcome every investment-minded individual to join us
                            in the Condotel Investment Opportunity.</p>
                        <p>
                            You can also freely advertise with us, exchange links with us, or be a member of our webring
